<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Our Projects - Cepha, LLC</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f7;
            color: #1d1d1f;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 20px; }
        
        nav { margin-bottom: 60px; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5; }
        nav a { text-decoration: none; color: #1d1d1f; font-weight: 500; margin-right: 20px; }
        nav a:hover { color: #0066cc; }
        nav .active { color: #0066cc; }

        h1 { font-size: 40px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -1px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        
        .project-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-left: 6px solid #86868b; /* Neutral grey for stealth mode */
        }

        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #f5f5f7;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #86868b;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        h2 { margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 28px; }
        p { color: #515154; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        
        footer { text-align: center; color: #86868b; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 60px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <nav>
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/projects" class="active">Projects</a>
            <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
        </nav>

        <h1>Our Projects</h1>

        <div class="project-card">
            <span class="status-badge">In Development</span>
            <h2>Project Rise</h2>
            <p><strong>Category:</strong> Health & Fitness</p>
            <p>
                A user-friendly mobile application designed to help gym goers of all levels, from total beginners to serious enthusiasts, improve their training performance and outcomes. Currently in closed alpha testing.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
            <span class="status-badge">In Development</span>
            <h2>Project Mountain</h2>
            <p><strong>Category:</strong> Strategy & Simulation</p>
            <p>
                A culturally authentic simulation focused on the survival dynamics of ancient communities. 
                Players manage their community's impact on the local environment, resource gathering, 
                crafting and building, with the goal of overall community prosperity. 
            </p>
            <p>
                Unlike traditional strategy games, conflict is driven by the challenge of inter-community cooperation 
                and resource scarcity rather than direct warfare or combat.
            </p>
        </div>

        <footer>
            &copy; 2026 Cepha, LLC.
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>